      "x": 53, "y": 633, "width": 410, "height": 94,
      "text": "Volume compaction (blob.compact):\n  1. Copy live needles to .cpx temp file\n  2. Rename .cpx → .dat (atomic)\n  3. Rebuild NeedleMap from new .dat\nDedup: sha1 hash of content → dedup index\nTiering: cold volumes → S3/GCS backend",
