      "x": 543, "y": 516, "width": 385, "height": 209,
      "text": "FilerStore interface methods:\n  InsertEntry(ctx, entry) error\n  UpdateEntry(ctx, entry) error\n  FindEntry(ctx, path) (*Entry, error)\n  ListDirectoryEntries(ctx, dir, ...) (chan *Entry)\n  DeleteEntry(ctx, path) error\n  DeleteFolderChildren(ctx, dir) error\n──────────────────────────────\nBackends: leveldb2 (default) · redis3\n  postgres2 · mysql2 · cassandra · memory",
      "originalText": "FilerStore interface methods:\n  InsertEntry(ctx, entry) error\n  UpdateEntry(ctx, entry) error\n  FindEntry(ctx, path) (*Entry, error)\n  ListDirectoryEntries(ctx, dir, ...) (chan *Entry)\n  DeleteEntry(ctx, path) error\n  DeleteFolderChildren(ctx, dir) error\n──────────────────────────────\nBackends: leveldb2 (default) · redis3\n  postgres2 · mysql2 · cassandra · memory",
