    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "ev_raft_cmds_txt",
      "x": 988, "y": 515, "width": 420, "height": 209,
      "text": "Raft command apply cycle:\n  1. Leader receives heartbeat from VolumeServer\n  2. Topology.ProcessJoinMessage() updates DataNode\n  3. If MaxVolumeId changes: Raft.Apply(MaxVolumeIdCmd)\n  4. FSM applies → EventBus publishes EventMaxVolumeId\n  5. MasterServer.handleFSMEvents() calls Topology.SetMaxVolumeId\n──────────────────────────────\nSequencer.NextFileId(count=1):\n  Pre-allocates batches of 10000 IDs\n  RaftSequencer persists via Raft log → crash-safe\n  Returns monotone global NeedleId",
      "originalText": "Raft command apply cycle:\n  1. Leader receives heartbeat from VolumeServer\n  2. Topology.ProcessJoinMessage() updates DataNode\n  3. If MaxVolumeId changes: Raft.Apply(MaxVolumeIdCmd)\n  4. FSM applies → EventBus publishes EventMaxVolumeId\n  5. MasterServer.handleFSMEvents() calls Topology.SetMaxVolumeId\n──────────────────────────────\nSequencer.NextFileId(count=1):\n  Pre-allocates batches of 10000 IDs\n  RaftSequencer persists via Raft log → crash-safe\n  Returns monotone global NeedleId",
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
